%% Data Flow Diagram for Guardrails Detectors
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
sequenceDiagram
    participant Orch as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant BuiltIn as Built-in Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Istio as Istio Sidecar<br/>mTLS STRICT
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Judge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3/Minio Storage<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant KServeSI as KServe Storage<br/>Initializer

    Note over KServeSI,S3: Flow 4: Model Download at Startup (HuggingFace)
    KServeSI->>S3: GET model artifacts<br/>9000/TCP HTTP plaintext<br/>Auth: AWS AccessKey/SecretKey
    S3-->>KServeSI: Model files
    KServeSI->>HF: Mount model to container

    Note over Orch,BuiltIn: Flow 1: Built-in Detection (PII, file-type, custom)
    Orch->>BuiltIn: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>8080/TCP HTTP plaintext<br/>Auth: None
    Note right of BuiltIn: Regex PII scan<br/>(email, CC, SSN, phone, IP)<br/>File-type validation<br/>Custom detector functions
    BuiltIn-->>Orch: Detection results<br/>(positions, scores, labels)

    Note over Orch,HF: Flow 2: HuggingFace Detection (via KServe + Istio)
    Orch->>Istio: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>8000/TCP
    Istio->>HF: Forward request<br/>mTLS encrypted<br/>Auth: mTLS client cert
    Note right of HF: ML model inference<br/>(SequenceClassification<br/>or GraniteForCausalLM)
    HF-->>Istio: Detection results
    Istio-->>Orch: Response<br/>mTLS encrypted

    Note over Orch,vLLM: Flow 3: LLM Judge Detection (via KServe + Istio + vLLM)
    Orch->>Istio: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>8000/TCP
    Istio->>Judge: Forward request<br/>mTLS encrypted<br/>Auth: mTLS client cert
    Judge->>vLLM: POST evaluation prompt<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>OpenAI-compatible API<br/>Istio mTLS within mesh
    vLLM-->>Judge: LLM evaluation response
    Note right of Judge: Score against metrics<br/>(safety, toxicity,<br/>accuracy, helpfulness)
    Judge-->>Istio: Detection results
    Istio-->>Orch: Response<br/>mTLS encrypted
